    <note type="biography">
        <p>Russian statistician. Attended university at Kharkov and St Petersburg from 1871, studying natural sciences. Studied statistics at the École des sciences anthropologiques in Paris during his five-year stay in France. Member of the council of the Société de statistique. After returning to St Petersburg, died of diphtheria.</p></note>
